snippet.title: ProjectAir
snippet.description:
DIY backyard aerospace engineering. I build planes, rocket, boats and other vehicles to push what you can make at home to the absolute limit! Each video is usually a new project, so subscribe to get them dropping into your feed every month! 

You can follow my projects as they come together on Instagram @jameswhomsley
For free plans, resources and bonus content, checkout my Patreon https://www.patreon.com/jameswhomsley

Business enquires, see address below👇
